    "121223532": {
      "title": "On a cubically convergent derivative free root finding method",
      "abstract": "Using a method for accelerating convergence and Weierstrass\u2019 correction, a cubically convergent method without derivatives for the simultaneous determination of polynomial zeros is derived. The proposed method possesses approximately the structure of Halley's method. Using the Gauss\u2013Seidel approach, the single-step method is outlined. Convergence analysis and computational aspects are reported."
    }
